      <text>This is for the lordlings out there who don't really
have much happening ICly or are simple looking
for a new direction for thier character.

The Band of the Red Hand WANTS YOU!

Any of you guys who've read up through book five
should remember that there are tons of Tairen and
Cairhienin nobility within the Band.  Not only that,
but all these lords hold high ranking military positions
as well.  I am willing to guild lords -as- high ranked
officers based on their backgrounds.  If this is some-
thing that would interest you, please contact me as
soon as you can.  If you don't want to bring your
current lord-type alt into the Band but it still sounds
like something that would be interesting, still contact
me please.  We can work something out fairly easily.
I'm posting this in an obvious (I would think) effort
to try and regain some activity within the guild and
provide more varied roleplay for people so... That is
my intention, not to simply empower a character but
to help the guild and the MUD in general by branching
out of the larger guilds.

I hope to hear from you soon :)

Thanks,
      Hartigan
</text>
